{"id":2043,"date":"2023-09-28T11:37:26","date_gmt":"2023-09-28T03:37:26","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/?page_id=2043"},"modified":"2023-12-29T12:18:38","modified_gmt":"2023-12-29T04:18:38","slug":"corporate-esg-2","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/en\/corporate-esg-2\/","title":{"rendered":"Corporate ESG (The ESG content provided is based on the 2021 version, and the 2022 edition is expected to be completed and updated in December.)"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>PlayNitride Inc. continues to deepen research and development in the field of MicroLED with a new and pioneering point of view, providing the most appropriate products in the MircoLED application field. With the expansion of operations and the expectations of stakeholders, PlayNitride Inc. launches the Sustainability Management (ESG) promotion plan, examines the company&#8217;s operating environments and risks, and at the same time, establishes a sound corporate governance and integrity management culture, and effectively protects the rights and interests of various stakeholders to demonstrate corporate value.&nbsp;&nbsp;The vision and objectives of the company are established by integrating with the business strategy of sustainability management.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Environmental Sustainability<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Carbon Emission Management<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In accordance with the ISO14064-1:2018 standard in 2022, we will conduct the quantification, supervision, reporting and confirmation or verification of greenhouse gas inventories or plans to disclose the clarity and consistency of the greenhouse gas inventory, and at the same time handle internal employee education and training courses, assist in the implementation of significant indirect emission analysis and related emission coefficient construction, compile the activity data of each base, perform internal verification operations, and write the company&#8217;s GHG inventory procedure documents, emission inventories and inventory reports.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1016\" height=\"886\" src=\"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/\u78b3\u6392\u653e\u91cf\u8868\u82f1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1778\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Supply chain management<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. <strong>Management of Hazardous Substances<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Suppliers are required to provide the &#8220;Commitment not to Use Prohibited or Restricted Substances in Environmental Regulations&#8221; and Safety Data Sheet (SDS) of products, parts and materials, etc., and the third notary unit test data report to confirm compliance with the RoHS\/REACH product hazardous substance standard requirements.&nbsp;&nbsp;We conduct regular audits of qualified suppliers to confirm environmental protection and the maintenance of the product hazardous substance management system.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. <strong>Conflict Minerals Management<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The products, parts and materials required of our suppliers do not contain conflict minerals (gold (Au), tantalum (Ta), tin (Sn), tungsten (W), cobalt (Co) and other minerals and derivatives originating in the Democratic Republic of the Congo (DRC) and its surrounding countries and regions.&nbsp;&nbsp;Suppliers are required to complete and submit the content to PlayNitride Inc. in accordance with the format of the Conflict Minerals Report Template (CMRT).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Waste Management<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The company follows the requirements of waste cleaning regulations, implements waste management, and obtains ISO14001 certification, and continues to operate according to the management system.&nbsp;&nbsp;In addition to the approval of the competent authority, the relevant business also declares the quantity of waste output, storage, removal and treatment by means of the network in accordance with the relevant regulations on waste clean-up and the norms of the Environmental Protection Bureau, and also entrusts qualified manufacturers recognized by the EPD to remove and dispose of the waste according to the treatment method described in the waste clean-up plan.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In the future, the company will continue to work towards process waste reduction, resource conservation, decrease in waste generation, material recycling and reuse, and relief in environmental load, and achieve the goal of waste reduction and resource recycling and reuse.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Environmental Safety and Health Education and Training<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In order to promote the safety and health management of activities, products, service processes and relevant stakeholders related to operations, the company establishes, implements and maintains the procedures and standards of the management system that meets the requirements of the ISO 45001 international standard, effectively manages any negative impact on safety and health or anything that does not comply with the regulations, and continuously improves safety and health performance.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>According to the requirements of the management system and regulations, the implementation of occupational safety and health education and training for each new employee, and the regular implementation of retraining, emergency response education and training, and relevant provisions for all employees, to deepen the concept of safety of colleagues.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The above is also included in the annual education and training plan for continuous implementation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>ISO Management System Certification (Please click on the link for licenses)<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:1\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ISO-9001.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ISO 9001 Certificate<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ISO14001.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ISO 14001 Certificate<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ISO-45001.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ISO 45001 Certificate<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Social Responsibility&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Popular Science Education&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The R&amp;D team in PlayNitride Inc. has the courage to challenge itself, continue to provide products and solutions for diverse application fields with technological innovation, and continue to promote the relevant knowledge of MicroLED fields, hoping that MicroLED can be implemented into our daily life faster.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The company not only participates in the corporate lectures and industry sharing invited by PIDA, but also cooperates with the physical, optoelectric, electrical and other science and engineering departments of various colleges and universities from time to time, in the form of school sharing or enterprise visits.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;For MicroLED development technology and related applications for thematic sharing courses, we not only enhance students&#8217; professional and technical knowledge, but also broaden students&#8217; vision of industry development, new technologies.&nbsp;&nbsp;The current number of cooperation sessions has registered more than 15 occasions, while many colleges and universities of related disciplines have paid visit to the factory.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In the process of visiting, in addition to the teaching of technology, we also demonstrate exhibits and do environment introduction, so that students can have a deeper contact with the entrepreneurial culture, workplace environment, company development, thus understanding MicroLED current development and application.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2364\" height=\"1774\" src=\"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ESG-2-1-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1510\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Department of Optoelectronic Engineering, Taipei University of Science and Technology &#8211; &#8220;Display Panel with Internship&#8221;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Department of Optoelectronic Engineering, Taipei University of Science and Technology &#8211; &#8220;Optoelectronic Industry Trend Analysis&#8221;&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>rofessional Lecture Sharing: Institute of Optoelectronic Engineering, National Normal University and Bachelor&#8217;s Program &#8211; &#8220;Optoelectronic Semiconductors&#8221;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Corporate Visit: The Institute of Optoelectronic Engineering, National Taiwan Normal University<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Corporate Visit: The School of Electrical Engineering of Yang Ming Chiao Tung University<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Corporate Visit: The Department of Optoelectronic Engineering, Yang Ming Chiao Tung University<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Corporate Visit: The Department of Materials, National Tsing Hua University-&#8220;Applied Optoelectronics&#8221;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Corporate Visit: The Department of Electronic Engineering of National Yunlin University of Science and Technology<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Corporate Visit: The Faculty of Electrical Engineering, Fu Jen University<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>(To be continued&#8230;)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Employee Care<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. <strong>COVID-19 Response Measures<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Hold epidemic prevention seminars, adjust epidemic prevention measures according to the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC), update epidemic prevention information regularly, and publish it to the cloud office for easy reference.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Colleagues who overlap with the confirmed person&#8217;s route and have symptoms of discomfort carry out health management, and adopt the methods of working from home, transferring work shift or asking for leave.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Restricted Visitors: Routine manufacturers and non-routine necessary factory entry must not be the same as the footprint of the confirmed person.&nbsp;&nbsp;Confirm the contact between the person entering the factory and the confirmed person.\n<ul>\n<li>Take Temperature<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Complete the Visitor and Contractor Awareness Symptom Declaration Form<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Scan Visitor QRCode<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. <strong>COVID-19 Epidemic Prevention Management<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1852\" height=\"1386\" src=\"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/\u9810\u9632\u7ba1\u7406\u82f1\u6587.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1739\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-rounded\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1395\" src=\"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/ESG-rapid-test-station-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1721\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>3. Shared Community Health and Safety<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>During the&nbsp;long weekend&nbsp;period, employees returned to the company from various counties and cities, and before the start of the&nbsp;long weekend&nbsp;period, we provided each colleague with fast-test reagents and alcohol wipes, and completed the self-test at home first to maintain the health and safety of the community and individuals.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>4. Employee Health Check &amp; Vaccine Insurance<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>The company provides health examination that is better than the regulations set by the government, and contacts the hospital to the factory every year to conduct health examinations for all employees.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Three days of paid welfare leave is provided from the date of arrival.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Provide after-service employee vaccine insurance:<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1816\" height=\"858\" src=\"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/\u4fdd\u96aa\u8868\u683c-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1815\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>5. Physical and Mental Health Management&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Conduct health care management according to needs, provide different professional assessments, physical and psychological consultations, and let supervisors informed, adjust and evaluate the work content.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Prevent abnormal workloads, special health hazards, maternal health protection, avoidance of human causes, elimination of workplace violence, employment of people with physical and mental disabilities, on-the-job medical services, and resumption of work by assessment personnel.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Encourage colleagues to manage their own health, regularly measure blood pressure and effectively prevent cardiovascular disease.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Public Welfare Participation<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. <strong>Sponsor the St. Francis Joint Exhortation Park Fair&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>In October 2020, the Company had the honor to participate in the St. Francis Joint Exhortation Park Tour held at the Miaoli Cat Meow Family Park.&nbsp;&nbsp;In cooperation with St. Francis Children&#8217;s and Children&#8217;s Centre, 200 garden passes were subscribed as benefits for employees&#8217; family activities, and the stalls were adopted to donate all the proceeds to the Children&#8217;s and Children&#8217;s Centre.&nbsp;&nbsp;This is a small activity to give back to the society, but it is not only the satisfaction of contributing love, but also the sense of achievement of colleagues working together to complete the task: from buying ingredients, preparing ingredients, cooking, loading, shipping, setting up stalls and selling&#8230; For us who have no experience, everything is the first time to be touched and challenged.&nbsp;&nbsp;The pursuit of innovation and excellence of the spirit of employees, embodied in every activity, from work performance, to small after-work activities, all show the power of &#8220;PlayNitride&#8221;.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2364\" height=\"1773\" src=\"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ESG-2-2-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1166\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ESG-2-2-1.jpg 2364w, https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ESG-2-2-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ESG-2-2-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ESG-2-2-1-2048x1536.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2364px) 100vw, 2364px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. <strong>PlayNitride Really Awesome Collaborating Hsinchu City Salutes the Sea \u2013 Beach Cleanup Activity for 2022<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>After two years of the epidemic, we once again promoted to join hand in hand to participate in Hsinchu City&#8217;s 2022 Salute to the Sea &#8211; Autumn Beach Cleanup Activity.&nbsp;&nbsp;Each colleague and his family members enthusiastically participated to make their own efforts to clean up the waste on the beach, and deeply experienced the necessity of environmental protection and ocean sustainability, and then led the people around them to serve the ocean and make the global environment we live in better.&nbsp;       <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8211; Event Date: 08:00 ~ 11:00 October 01, 2022   <br>&#8211; Venue: Main cleanup site: Fortune Sand Bay \/ Sub-cleanup site: Area B \u00a0                                                                                             <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/\u6de8\u7058\u7167\u72472022-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1766\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. <strong>2020 Launch Response to Earth Hour 60+<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The company is committed to becoming the integrated role of MicroLED Display Ecosystem.&nbsp;&nbsp;Employees in the daily work promote the environmental protection of the spontaneous green behavior, including the first day of the job to distribute environmentally friendly tableware and bags for their use.&nbsp;&nbsp;Colleagues delight in sharing the commute, readily turn off unnecessary lights and power consumption products, etc.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The company is deeply rooted in sustainability issues, but also invites colleagues to face up to climate change.&nbsp;&nbsp;In 2020, the company also attended the international &#8220;Earth Hour 60+ Earth Hour&#8221;.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;At the event, our CEO Dr. Charles Li led the company&#8217;s working partners hold up signs to jointly respond to Earth Hour and shoot videos and photos to promote it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2850\" height=\"1588\" src=\"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ESG-2-2-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1178\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ESG-2-2-4.png 2850w, https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ESG-2-2-4-768x428.png 768w, https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ESG-2-2-4-1536x856.png 1536w, https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ESG-2-2-4-2048x1141.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2850px) 100vw, 2850px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Human Rights Policy<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Company abides by relevant labor laws and regulations and upholds the human rights of all employees, including full-time employees, contract and temporary workers, and interns, and creates a dignified working environments.&nbsp;&nbsp;The company recognizes and supports internationally recognized human rights standards such as the United Nations Universal Declaration of Human Rights, the United Nations Global Covenant, the United Nations Guiding Principles on Business and Human Rights, and the United Nations International Labor Organization, treats and respects all personnel with dignity, and implements the Human Rights Management Policy for PlayNitride Inc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Human Rights Management Approach<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Provide a safe and healthy working environment free from harassmen<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Eliminate illegal discrimination and ensure equality of working opportunities<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ban on child labor<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ban on forced labor<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Foster an environment that encourages communication and set up an open management model<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Support and assist employees with maintaining their physical\/mental well-being and work-life balance<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Regularly inspect and evaluate related schemes and practices<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Master Lectures<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>With the talent adaptive learning and development system to move the Company towards the road of sustainable management, we put great emphasis on the growth and cultivation of employees by providing prospective, diversified education and training, strengthening the professional ability of employees in the workplace, in order to create an environment for learning and growing together.&nbsp;&nbsp;The Company will also regularly organize internal lectures, to provide colleagues with different aspects of learning and brainstorming.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Special invitation was given to the Father of Blue-light, Dr. Shuji Nakamura for the first grand innovation lecture of 2019.<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>In order to enhance the personal quality and self-growth of colleagues, the Company launched a series of PlayNitride seminars by inviting outstanding personage from various fields to communicate and share with working partners.&nbsp;&nbsp;For the first lecture, we invited the Nobel Laureate in Physics known as the Father of Blue-light Dr. Shuji Nakamura to give a speech.&nbsp;&nbsp;In Dr. Nakamura&#8217;s sharing, we learned about the many problems he encountered in the research and development process, and how to overcome these obstacles to develop blue light-emitting diodes.&nbsp;&nbsp;After the speech, the Company&#8217;s executives also went deep into a symposium with Dr. Nakamura, and also exchanged our current development and the difficulties encountered through the product exhibits.&nbsp;&nbsp;The above brief exchange and sharing has injected a lot of energy into the Company and encouraged our R&amp;D engineers to continue to move forward firmly on the road of MicroLED.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ESG-2-2-4-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1175\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ESG-2-2-4-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/www.playnitride.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/ESG