sp;It will also have a mutually exclusive effect under limited resources, thus requiring gradual planning from the process of company operation to execute implementation.&nbsp;&nbsp;Therefore, in the process of engaging with various important stakeholders, we also examine the relevance of various stakeholders and PlayNitride, contemplate the purpose and focus of the response, and then bring about short-term practices and long-term strategic objectives.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>PlayNitride Inc. continues to deepen research and development in the field of MicroLED with a new and pioneering point of view, providing the most appropriate products in the MircoLED application field. With the expansion of operations and the expectations of stakeholders, PlayNitride Inc. launches the Sustainability Management (ESG) promotion plan, examines the company&#8217;s operating environments [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","template":"","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v18.1 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Corporate ESG (The ESG content provided is based on the 2021 version, and the 2022 edition is expected to be completed and updated in December.) - PlayNitride - \u933c\u5275\u79d1\u6280<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"PlayNitride \u900f\u904e\u5275\u65b0\u7684\u7814\u767c\u6280\u8853\u548c\u591a\u5143\u7684\u5546\u696d\u6a21\u5f0f\uff0c\u73fe\u5df2\u6210\u70ba MicroLED \u6280\u8853\u9818\u57df\u7684\u9818\u5c0e\u5ee0\u5546\u4e4b\u4e00\uff0c\u4e26\u81ea\u884c\u958b\u767c\u51fa PixeLED Display\u3001SMAR\u00b7Tech \u4fee\u88dc\u3001PixeLED Matrix \u6a21\u7d44\u5316\u3001\u00b5-PixeLED \u5fae\u986f\u793a\u5668\u7b49\u6280\u8853\u3002\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-